text: Krasny Oktyabr () is a rural locality (a village) in Mrakovsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 11 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Krasnousolsky, 4 km from Mrakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Krasny Oktyabr, Gafuriysky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
